    "visibility_markdown": "## M-1 Outcomes\n\nObservational — settlement tracking; registered verdict metric is excess CLV.\nOutcome denominator basis: PA-valid settled player-market rows only; zero-PA and absent-boxscore rows are VOID.\nRetroactive-grading note: CLV sign is rendered from captured closes where available; this is report visibility only.\n\n### 2026-07-13 settlements\n\nNo settled M-1 picks found.\n\n### Cumulative M-1 outcomes through 2026-07-13\n\n| Market | Picks | Hits | Hit rate | Avg implied prob at pick |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Doubles | 446 | 65 | 14.6% | 18.7% |\n| Hits | 572 | 309 | 54.0% | 57.4% |\n| HR | 345 | 47 | 13.6% | 14.8% |\n| Total bases | 753 | 300 | 39.8% | 45.2% |\n\nHR subgroup (secondary only; no HR-specific verdict): matched-close coverage=310/345 (89.9%); unmatched=35.\n\n#### Cumulative CLV-sign split\n\n| Market | CLV bucket | Picks | Hits | Hit rate |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Doubles | negative/flat CLV | 256 | 35 | 13.7% |\n| Doubles | positive CLV | 139 | 27 | 19.4% |\n| Hits | negative/flat CLV | 303 | 156 | 51.5% |\n| Hits | positive CLV | 199 | 118 | 59.3% |\n| HR | negative/flat CLV | 143 | 12 | 8.4% |\n| HR | positive CLV | 167 | 29 | 17.4% |\n| Total bases | negative/flat CLV | 406 | 159 | 39.2% |\n| Total bases | positive CLV | 274 | 114 | 41.6% |\n\n## Sim-1 Outcomes\n\nObservational — settlement tracking; registered verdict metric is excess CLV.\nSim-1 remains passive/unscored shadow archive; this is report-window visibility only, not a registered read.\n\n| Date | Top-3 hits | Top-3 hit rate | Top-3 hit names | Top-10 hits | Top-10 hit rate | Top-10 hit names |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 2026-07-02 | 0/3 | 0.0% | none | 0/10 | 0.0% | none |\n| 2026-07-03 | 2/3 | 66.7% | Kody Clemens, Junior Caminero | 2/9 | 22.2% | Kody Clemens, Junior Caminero |\n| 2026-07-04 | 1/3 | 33.3% | Jackson Chourio | 3/10 | 30.0% | Jackson Chourio, Dominic Canzone, Kody Clemens |\n| 2026-07-05 | 1/3 | 33.3% | Rafael Dever